
## Part 7: Reporting System

The module uses Odoo's QWeb engine ([report/](file:///c:/odoo-addons/ensa_hoceima_hr/models/internship.py#77-82)) to generate high-quality PDF documents.

### 1. Report Actions ([report/report_actions.xml](file:///c:/odoo-addons/ensa_hoceima_hr/report/report_actions.xml))
*   Define the "Print" menu item in the Action dropdown.
*   Example: `action_report_internship_certificate` binds to `ensa.internship`.

### 2. Templates
*   **Base Layout** ([ensah_report_base.xml](file:///c:/odoo-addons/ensa_hoceima_hr/report/ensah_report_base.xml)): Defines the common header (ENSAH Logo, Address) and footer. All other reports inherit this using `<t t-call="ensa_hoceima_hr.ensah_report_layout">`.
*   **Certificate** ([professional_reports.xml](file:///c:/odoo-addons/ensa_hoceima_hr/report/professional_reports.xml)): Uses a background image (`certificate_border.png`) and absolute positioning to create a diploma-like feel. It dynamically injects the Student Name, Director's Signature, and Date.

